                    p Organizations today are facing problems of unprecedented scale and complexity.  These are the problems we think technology and data can help to solve. This is why we’ve created Quorum; to create positive social change and empower people though technology. But we need to look at the future and these news goals & opportunities without forgetting our core values. 
                    ul
