                        li EMANCIPATE DATA 
                        li OPEN SOFWARE
                        li ACHIEVE OUTCOMES AND GET REAL IMPACT
                        li TECHNOLOGY HAVE TO ADAPT TO HUMAN, NOT THE OTHER WAY AROUND
